Package: db41
Version: 4.1.25
Revision: 18
Source: http://www.sleepycat.com/update/snapshot/db-%v.NC.tar.gz
Replaces: db, db3, db31 (<< 3.1.17-8), db4-ssl, db4, db41-ssl
